{{2004 Big East football standings}}
The '''2004 Pittsburgh Panthers football team''' represented the [[University of Pittsburgh]] in the 2004 college football season in which they won a share of The [[Big East Conference]] Championship and were awarded with a [[Bowl Championship Series|BCS]] berth to the [[2005 Fiesta Bowl]].

